parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unwanted activation of the automatic emergency braking system can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or slow down, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions or other accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or slows down without warning
often with no apparent obstacle or hazard in front of the vehicle. The brake warning light may flash
and the vehicle may come to a complete stop or slow down significantly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: False Collision Mitigation Braking System Alerts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false alerts from the collision mitigation braking system can cause unnecessary panic and potentially lead to accidents, as the driver may react suddenly to the alert.
symptoms: The collision mitigation braking system warning light comes on
and the vehicle may brake or slow down unnecessarily
even when there is no apparent obstacle or hazard in front of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of ADAS, including the collision mitigation braking system, can lead to a loss of vehicle control and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ADAS warning lights come on
and the systems may malfunction or fail to operate properly
including the collision mitigation braking system
adaptive cruise control
and lane departure warning systems.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Braking/False Activation of Automatic Emergency Braking (AEB) System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended braking can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or slows down without any obstacles or vehicles in front
sometimes with warning lights or beeping sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake System Failure/Wear and Tear Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake system failure can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle is unable to stop in time.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake system warning lights are illuminated
or the brakes are worn out prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake pedal simulator failure can cause the brake system to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal simulator fails
causing the brake system to malfunction
and the vehicle may not be able to stop in time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The emergency brake switch failure can cause the brake system to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The emergency brake switch fails
causing the brake system warning lights to be illuminated
and the vehicle may not be able to stop in time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake hold system failure can cause the vehicle to creep forward or roll unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake hold system fails to hold the vehicle in place
causing it to creep forward or roll unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and safety risks, especially in hot weather conditions.
symptoms: AC not working
hissing noise
vibration in the seats.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty fuel pump can cause engine stalling, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Loud noise from the fuel pump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the door lock actuator can cause doors to unlock or not lock, compromising vehicle security.
symptoms: Intermittent or permanent failure of door lock actuators
doors unlocking or not locking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the electrical and infotainment systems can cause distractions, discomfort, and safety risks.
symptoms: Screen turning off and on
humming noise from the speaker system
loud humming noise at 52mph.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake and Collision Mitigation System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the brake and collision mitigation systems can cause accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration
lurching
or loss of control
brake mitigation system activating unnecessarily
collision mitigation system not responding.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rattling and noise issues can cause discomfort and distractions while driving.
symptoms: Rattling noise from the dashboard and rear deck
loud humming noise
loud roaring noise in cold weather.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the tire pressure monitoring system can cause tire blowouts or accidents.
symptoms: Tire sensor light coming on despite proper tire pressure.
